This is the default [[sound sequence]] for opening an [[animated door]] with the DORQTR01, DORIRS01, or DORALN01 texture in ''[[Strife]]''. It is also redirected from [[DoorAirlock]].
==== [[SNDSEQ]] definition ==== :DoorOpenAirlock play doors/airlock_open nostopcutoff end [[Category:Sound sequences]]
